title: Pukanec is Slovakia’s black mulberry capital
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
The former royal town, Pukanec, has a rich history of mining, pottery and growing vines. But the story of Samko Šikeť of Pukanec is a whole new story.   
 
Presenter: Anna Fay 
Guest: Peter Dlhopolec
